{"tid":381551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★灣仔搜兩大廈掃黃","createTime":"2017-08-31T04:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T06:05:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8647dbb9d4fdc1eadfe1deeb3ca675913450b09b","tid":381551,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"警方繼續進行「雷霆17」反罪惡行動，晚上8時許，灣仔警區刑事部與特別職務隊，聯同入境處職員，展開代號「虎尾」的掃黃行動，突擊搜查駱克道381號富士大廈及474號兩幢大廈多個單位，拘捕17名內地女子﹝18至41歲），疑涉及賣淫勾當，他們俱持雙程證來港，疑違反逗留條件，稍後交由入境處跟進。行動中，警方檢獲一批避孕套、漱口水及濕滑劑等證物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830231200901-0830_00822_001_02b.jpg?20170831014854\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830231200901-0830_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20170831014854&h=a796baa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/bkn-20170830231200901-0830_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170830%2Fbkn-20170830231200901-0830_00822_001.html&d=95kRaKE2A%2FWIR7VeuoWqUv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f4eab624\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/bkn-20170830231200901-0830_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9c78bc79ec3a471e1241f1d4a2dae94f6a81d2c4","tid":381551,"uid":71479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5884b2776234242e1db8c2b549ba3e302af3cf8","tid":381551,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:58:29.000Z","msg":"自從追 游b還錢後，突然多左掃黃，有冇關係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9749bf215929ac5bd36955989c0567b2b515ab","tid":381551,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:59:50.000Z","msg":"灣仔掃黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /